<h1>About</h1>

<br />
<body>
    <p>
        I created this website because I, like most people, like to save money. <br/>
        As a student, one of my biggest expenses each semester is all of the textbooks <br/>
        you are required to buy. In most cases, these $150 textbooks sat unused on my desk <br/>
        for the entire semester! What a waste! So I thought, if only there was an easy way to <br/>
        research who has the best prices on all of my textbook. <br/>
        So to make your life easier, you can use this webapp to easily check the prices of <br/>
        certain textbooks from all of the top online and retail booksellers. <br/>
        The hard part is finding someone to buy all of your like new textbooks at the end of <br/>
        semester. Stay tuned, that functionality may be coming soon. <br/>
    </p>
